@page "/consulting"

<PageTitle>Consulting – Xipe</PageTitle>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-photo" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553877522-43269d4ea984?w=1920&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80'); opacity: 0.25;"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-badge">AI &amp; Technology Consulting</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
            Strategic advisory<br />
            for <em>AI-driven</em><br />
            products.
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
            Some technology decisions are too important to figure out by trial and error.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-subtitle-2">
            At Xipe, we advise companies on how to design, build, and evolve software systems in the age of artificial intelligence.
        </p>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn-hero">Request an advisory session &rarr;</a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT WE ADVISE ON -->
<section id="advise">
    <div class="inner">
        <span class="advise-label">What We Advise On</span>
        <h2 class="advise-title">Senior judgment.<br />Where it matters most.</h2>
        <p class="advise-intro">We typically work with founders, executives, and product leaders on decisions such as:</p>
        <div class="advise-grid">
            <div class="advise-card">
                <div class="advise-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-cpu"></i></div>
                <h3>AI Strategy</h3>
                <p>How artificial intelligence should shape your product and operations; from model selection to implementation roadmap.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="advise-card">
                <div class="advise-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-diagram-3"></i></div>
                <h3>Software Architecture</h3>
                <p>Designing systems that scale and remain maintainable; built to evolve with your business, not against it.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="advise-card">
                <div class="advise-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-compass"></i></div>
                <h3>Product Technology Strategy</h3>
                <p>Aligning product vision with technical execution; so your roadmap is ambitious and grounded in reality.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="advise-card">
                <div class="advise-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-gear"></i></div>
                <h3>Engineering Systems</h3>
                <p>Improving how teams design, build, and ship software; faster cycles, higher quality, less overhead.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ADVISORY SESSIONS -->
<section id="sessions">
    <div class="inner">
        <div>
            <span class="sessions-label">Advisory Sessions</span>
            <h2 class="sessions-title">Designed for moments where <em>clarity matters</em> more than speed.</h2>
            <p class="sessions-body">Our consulting is structured around high-impact sessions that give you direct access to senior technical judgment; shaped by years of building and operating real software platforms.</p>
            <ul class="sessions-list">
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Architecture and technology reviews</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> AI opportunity assessments</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Product technology strategy</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Development system audits</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/#contact" class="btn-sessions">Request a quote &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sessions-callout">
            <p>More than 15 years of experience.</p>
            <strong>Designing production software used by real businesses; combined with modern AI-augmented development practices.</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- SENIOR PRACTITIONERS -->
<section id="practitioners">
    <div class="inner">
        <div>
            <span class="prac-label">Who You Work With</span>
            <h2 class="prac-title">Work directly with <em>senior specialists.</em></h2>
            <p class="prac-body">When you engage with Xipe, you work with engineers and product strategists who have spent years designing and operating real software platforms.</p>
            <p class="prac-body">It's guidance from people who have spent years solving real problems in production environments; not consultants reading from a playbook.</p>
            <p class="prac-body">Our role is simple: help you make the right technology decisions before they become expensive mistakes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="prac-callout">
            <p>You bring the question.</p>
            <strong>We bring the experience to answer it with confidence.</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FINAL CTA -->
<section id="final-cta">
    <div class="cta-glow"></div>
    <div class="inner">
        <span class="cta-label">Start the Conversation</span>
        <h2 class="cta-title">The right advice<br /><em>at the right time.</em></h2>
        <p class="cta-body">
            If you're evaluating AI opportunities, designing a new platform, or facing a critical technology decision; we'd be glad to help.
        </p>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn-hero">Contact the team &rarr;</a>
    </div>
</section>
